        <h1 class="label">Biography</h1>
        <div class="govspeak">
<p>Ian Hewett was appointed Director of Service Delivery, APHA in July 2017.</p>

<p>His previous roles include:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Deputy Director for the Transformational Change Directorate, Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs (Defra)</li>
  <li>Operations Director, Rural Payments Agency (RPA)</li>
  <li>Change Director, Rural Payments Agency (RPA)</li>
</ul>
</div>
      </section>

